title: HackRF BladeRF RTLSDR FUNcube dongle
extract: RTL-SDR vs Funcube PRO+ Dongle. ... The FCD+ is a software defined radio similar to the rtl-sdr, but with better overall performance. The video shows that the Funcube Dongle PRO+ has significantly less interference when tuning to a weaker radio station right next to a strong local station.May 24, 2013
